description:
Everyone from business leaders who want their companies to get better results; to managers who want better results from themselves and their employees; to entrepreneurs seeking increased productivity, success, and goal achievement will benefit from the knowledge and positive direction within this course

To maximize your personal productivity, wouldn't it be great to have your own personal coach there to give you a jump-start every day so that you start each day off with a positive frame of mind and course of action? Of course it would! No one wakes up and says, "I'm going to be ineffective and as pitiful as I can be today." We all want to be the best, but sometimes we just don't know where to start.This course provides a framework to enable you to take action today and every day going forward.
title: Productivity: achieve your dreams and goals
